      "text": "Broker / Topic 'orders'\n─────────────\nP0  append-only log\nP1  append-only log\nP2  append-only log\nP3  append-only log\n─────────────\nPartitionCount=4\nIsCompacted=false\nhash(key)%4 · MD5\noffset = _log.Count",
